      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·008.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">相鼠.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>相鼠有皮，人而無儀，人而無儀，不死何為。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Look at a rat, - it has its skin;
But a man should be without dignity of demeanour.
If a man have no dignity of demeanour,
What should he but die?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-008__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879-fulltext">
