      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·008.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">相鼠.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>相鼠有齒，人而無止，人而無止，不死何俟。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Look at a rat, - it has its teeth;
But a man shall be without any right deportment.
If a man have not right deportment,
What should he wait for but death?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
