      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·008.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">相鼠.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>相鼠有體，人而無禮，人而無禮，胡不遄死。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Look at a rat, - it has its limbs;
But a man shall be without any rules of propriety.
If a man observe no rules of propriety,
Why does he not quickly die?</seg>
      </tuv>
